<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Point Mckay</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Originally a part of the town of Montgomery, Point Mckay is a highly desirable residential neighborhood in the North West Calgary. </p>
            <p class="par-xl">Nestled along the banks of the Bow River, the community in Point McKay offers a great quality of life within a tranquil setting of immaculate greens, idyllic walking and cycling trails and breathtaking views of the river valley. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">With the nearby Riverside Club offering an entire range of activities including an adult fitness pool, a salt water pool and indoor tennis court, the residents have plentiful options to stay engaged.</p>
        </div>
